&lt;li&gt;Linus Torvalds&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/blockquote&gt;

&lt;p style="text-align: right;"&gt;De: &lt;a href="http://www.junauza.com/2010/12/top-50-programming-quotes-of-all-time.html" target="_blank"&gt;http://www.junauza.com/2010/12/top-50-programming-quotes-of-all-time.html&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href="http://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Linus_Torvalds_-_entering_dunk_tank_at_linux.conf.au_2004.jpg"&gt;&lt;img class="size-medium wp-image-2993" title="800px-Linus_Torvalds_-_entering_dunk_tank_at_linux.conf.au_2004" src="http://www.juanjoconti.com.ar/wp-content/uploads/2010/12/800px-Linus_Torvalds_-_entering_dunk_tank_at_linux.conf_.au_2004-300x203.jpg" alt="" width="300" height="203"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
