&lt;p&gt;BTW, Linus tiene un libro llamado &lt;a href="http://www.thinkgeek.com/books/nonfiction/38b2/" target="_blank"&gt;Just for fun&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>citas</category><category>General</category><category>Linus</category><category>programación</category><category>programadores</category><guid>http://www.juanjoconti.com.ar/posts/2010/12/15/just-for-fun.html</guid><pubDate>Wed, 15 Dec 2010 20:00:40 GMT</pubDate></item></channel></rss>